<p><strong>One complete reference · How everything works · April 2026</strong></p>
<hr>
<p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Your complete reference for how the platform works, what every screen does, how to demo it, and what to do next.</p>
<p><strong>Audience:</strong> Dave Cameron — founder, operator, demo lead</p>
<p><strong>Platform:</strong> CuraLive on Replit · 110 routers · 208 tables · 211 pages · Health 100%</p>
<p><strong>Published URL:</strong> https://curalive-platform.replit.app</p>
<p><strong>Demo target:</strong> Lumi Global partner meeting — week of 7 April 2026</p>
<p><strong>Exit target:</strong> $80M–$120M strategic acquisition · 24–36 months from commercial launch</p>
